      "side": 1,
      "message": "One concern is that, since we \"don\u0027t know\" what triggers we care about in this file, the scheduler sends no data for a given trigger until it actually triggers.  If the scheduler restarts more often than the trigger file appears, we\u0027ll almost always be in a \"no data\" state.",
